<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200804/2d495e945ace4e4b8ce607e637589310.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">130寸大屏画面</span></img></p>
